  "notes": "Cannot damage enemies that spawn already slag-element.\nStrong on Gaige: Close Enough can ricochet missed shots into nearby foes, spreading slag.\nA 11/05/13 hotfix increased its magazine size and damage (along with other Bandit SMGs).\nCommonly dropped by Jimbo and Tector Hodunk if you side with the Zafords in Clan Wars, locking you out of fighting Mick Zaford for the Maggie.\nYou can farm both in one playthrough: side with Zafords, kill only Jimbo and Tector, check the drop, then save-quit before the mission becomes turn-in ready to reset the choice.",
